	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Jul 26th 12:10 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Could someone explain to my why we would want to use the Symbol of Transal Spell instead of Healing (at level 14) The Healing spell gives a minimum of 84 HP up to 100 at level 30. Whereas the Symbol of Transal Increases total and current HP by a minimum of 34 up to 73 at level 21, PLUS you need a Cat's Eye Agate in order to cast it. Is there any advantage?<br><br>Kerridwen<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
